* SQL Instructions\nand Examples
** SQL expressions
***_ Define reusable business concepts
***_ Measures: gross margin calculation
***_ Dimensions: fiscal quarter from date
** Example SQL queries
***_ Question + SQL answer pairs
***_ Address domain-specific phrasing
***_ Parameters with :parameter_name syntax
***_ Marked as Trusted responses
** Text instructions (general)
***_ Global context across all questions
***_ Fiscal year start, timezone rules
***_ Use sparingly
** Limit: 100 instructions total
